   { "text" : "As a young man, I frequently sought out exhilarating experiences, craving the adrenaline rush of life's novelties, while as a responsible adult, I've come to understand the profound value of accumulated wisdom and life experience." }
], "model_id" : "cross-encoder/ms-marco-minilm-l-12-v2" , "project_id" : "{project_id}" } Copy to clipboard Run the following curl request. Replace {token} and {JSON-file} with your values. curl -X POST                                                     \
-H "Authorization: Bearer {token}" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
<your-service-url>/ml/v1/text/rerank?version=2024-05-31 \
--data "@{JSON-file}" Copy to clipboard Sample output: {
